.TH rewinddir 3 2022-12-15 "Linux man-pages 6.03"
.SH NAME
rewinddir \- reset directory stream
.SH LIBRARY
Standard C library
.RI ( libc ", " \-lc )
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.B #include <sys/types.h>
.B #include <dirent.h>
.PP
.BI "void rewinddir(DIR *" dirp );
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.BR rewinddir ()
function resets the position of the directory
stream
.I dirp
to the beginning of the directory.
.SH RETURN VALUE
The
.BR rewinddir ()
function returns no value.
